73
00:04:09,070 --> 00:04:11,210
suddenly they have bloomed so much.

74
00:04:11,470 --> 00:04:13,760
The most surprising thing is that people,

75
00:04:13,960 --> 00:04:15,890
say, even from Switzerland

76
00:04:16,090 --> 00:04:18,080
who do not know a word of Sanskrit,

77
00:04:18,280 --> 00:04:20,135
